 services that merchants have the option to subscribe. It serves users and merchants through PayPay brand names. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Shinjuku, Japan.", "Address": "Yotsuya Tower, Shinjuku, Japan, 160-0004", "AddressData": {"Street": "Yotsuya Tower", "City": "Shinjuku", "Country": "Japan", "ZIP": "160-0004"}, "Listings": {}, "Officers": {"0": {"Name": "Mr. Ichiro  Nakayama", "Title": "President, CEO, Corporate Officer & Representative Director", "YearBorn": "1969"}, "1": {"Name": "Mr. Wataru  Kagechika", "Title": "Managing Corporate Officer & CFO", "YearBorn": "1974"}, "2": {"Name": "Mr. Hajime  Baba", "Title": "Executive VP, Co-COO & Corporate Officer", "YearBorn": "1965"}, "3": {"Name": "Mr. Masamichi  Yasuda", "Title": "Executive VP, Co-COO & Corporate Officer", "YearBorn": "1960"}, "4": {"Name": "Mr. Masanori  Sode", "Title": "Managing Corporate Officer, Chief Administrative Officer & Chief Human Resource Officer", "YearBorn": "1963"}, "5": {"Name": "Mr. Hirofumi  Fujii", "Title": "Corporate Officer, CMO, Head of the Mrkt Strategy Div & Business Operations Group", "YearBorn": "NA"}, "6": {"Name": "Mr. Yosuke  Terada", "Title": "CCO, CRO, DPO & Corporate Officer", "YearBorn": "NA"}}, "Phone": "81 3 6885 8181", "WebURL": "https://paypay.ne.jp", "LogoURL": "", "FullTimeEmployees": 2012, "UpdatedAt": "2026-04-12"}, "Highlights": {"MarketCapitalization": 13439372288, "MarketCapitalizationMln": 13439.3723, "EBITDA": 77529997312, "PERatio": 19.1429, "PEGRatio": null, "WallStreetTargetPrice": 25.527, "BookValue": 2.8106, "DividendShare": null, "DividendYield": null, "EarningsShare": 1.05, "EPSEstimateCurrentYear": 185.7348, "EPSEstimateNextYear": 115.5861, "EPSEstimateNextQuarter": 0, "EPSEstimateCurrentQuarter": 0, "MostRecentQuarter": "2025-12-31", "ProfitMargin": 0.3128, "OperatingMarginTTM": 0.2476, "ReturnOnAssetsTTM": 0, "ReturnOnEquityTTM": 0, "RevenueTTM": 355530014720, "RevenuePerShareTTM": 578.993, "QuarterlyRevenueGrowt